                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-440-18600507 t18600507-440-punishment-50"></join>Four Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">BROOKS</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18600507-440-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
