                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">THIRD COURT</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">Thursday, May</hi> 10<hi rend="italic">th</hi>, 1860.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">PRESENT</hi>—Mr. Ald. <hi rend="smallCaps">CUBITT</hi>; Mr. Ald. <hi rend="smallCaps">CONDER</hi>; and Mr. <hi rend="smallCaps">COMMON SERJEANT</hi>.</p>
